t en place, le duel peut commencer...La conclusion du cycle Mister Blueberry, un événement digne de la série, l'une des plus passionnantes aventures de la bande dessinée par le maître incontesté, Jean Giraud.", "cover": "http://bdi.dlpdomain.com/album/9782205056426/couv/M1200x900/blueberry-tome-28-dust.jpg", "samples": ["http://bdi.dlpdomain.com/album/9782205056426/page1/M1200x900/blueberry-tome-28-dust.jpg", "http://bdi.dlpdomain.com/album/9782205056426/page2/M1200x900/blueberry-tome-28-dust.jpg", "http://bdi.dlpdomain.com/album/9782205056426/page3/M1200x900/blueberry-tome-28-dust.jpg", "http://bdi.dlpdomain.com/album/9782205056426/page4/M1200x900/blueberry-tome-28-dust.jpg", "http://bdi.dlpdomain.com/album/9782205056426/page5/M1200x900/blueberry-tome-28-dust.jpg", "http://bdi.dlpdomain.com/album/9782205056426/page6/M1200x900/blueberry-tome-28-dust.jpg", "http://bdi.dlpdomain.com/album/9782205056426/page7/M1200x900/blueberry-tome-28-dust.jpg", "http://bdi.dlpdomain.com/album/9782205056426/page8/M1200x900/blueberry-tome-28-dust.jpg", "http://bdi.dlpdomain.com/album/9782205056426/page9/M1200x900/blueberry-tome-28-dust.jpg"], "pages": 72, "date": "2005-03-25", "price": {"amount": 12.0, "currency": "eur"}, "ean": "9782205056426", "illustrators": ["Jean Giraud"], "writers": ["Jean Giraud"], "website": "http://www.dargaud.com/bd/Blueberry/Blueberry", "age": 9, "genre": ["western"], "width": 225, "height": 298}
